    'met-spec-title': 'Your exact position in the spectrum',
    'met-spec-sub': 'Within the operational axis, there are 9 precision positions. Not all ERA 2s are equal — a company with a score of 2.5 and one with 3.4 need completely different roadmaps. The 3GI Diagnosis places you exactly.',
    'met-era1-header': 'ERA 1 — Operational Chaos',
    'met-era1m-desc': 'Everything in the owner\'s head. No written processes or tools. Zero documentation.',
    'met-era1-desc': 'There\'s Excel but each person has their own. The information exists — nobody shares or uses it to make decisions.',
    'met-era1p-desc': 'Tools adopted, but they don\'t talk to each other. Data trapped in silos with no integration.',
