    'met-era3p-desc': 'AI as a structural competitive advantage. The system learns and improves without manual intervention.',
    'met-spec-note': '<strong>The 3GI Diagnosis identifies your exact sub-level</strong> — not just the ERA. That precision defines the right roadmap from day one.',
    'met-spec-cta': 'Discover my sub-level →',
    'met-stages-intro': 'Every company starts from a different point. The methodology allows entry at the right phase: some companies go through the whole journey, others start at Phase 2 or Phase 3. The important thing is to never skip the diagnosis.',
    'met-diag-name': 'Diagnosis · Diagnosis Report',
    'met-diag-badge': 'Free',
    'met-diag-desc': 'A 15-minute form where we identify your company\'s 3 biggest operational pain points and AI potential. Within 24–48 hours you receive a Diagnosis Report with the current gap vs. ideal state, the processes with the greatest opportunity, and the recommended next step.',
